[I] A Zig language server

[T] The Zig Language Server (ZLS) is a tool that implements Microsoft's
[T] Language Server Protocol for Zig in Zig. In simpler terms: it'll
[T] provide you with completions, go-to definition, etc.
[T] when you write Zig code!

[U] https://github.com/zigtools/zls/

